articles.title: West Indies complete 3-0 T20I series rout of South Africa - Hindustan Times
articles.description: West Indies complete 3-0 T20I series rout of South Africa | Crickit
articles.content:
The West Indies completed a 3-0 sweep of their T20I series with South Africa after an eight wicket crushing of the Proteas at Sabina Park on Sunday.
